; https://github.com/tldr-pages/tldr/blob/master/pages/osx/tag.md

% tag, osx

# Add tags to a file
tag <__a___add_> <tag_name1_tag_name2____> <path_to_file>

# Remove a tag
tag <__r___remove_> <tag_name> <path_to_file>

# Remove all tags from a file
tag <__r___remove_> \* <path_to_file>

# Show all files with a given tag
tag <__m___match_> <tag_name>
